Description:
WHEN WORDS FAIL!
If it's size, superb craftsmanship and finish that you're looking for in a home, then look no further!
This architect designed home boasts a terra cotta tiled roof, 2.7m ceilings throughout, quality window furnishings, ducted heating, cooling and vacuum systems, polished timber floors, quality carpets, camera intercom and security systems. There are three bedrooms, study nook, full ensuite to master, formal lounge with gas log fireplace and high gloss kitchen/meals area with Caesar stone benchtops, glass splash backs and dishwasher. A large, bright North facing family room opens to a rear decked outdoor entertainment area and alfresco sunroom. Solar panels greatly reduce energy costs. The double garage with automatic doors connects a separate workshop/storage room.
All this on a separate Title of approximately 462m2 in one of the best Central locations only a short walk to the CBD!
LOW MAINTENANCE, SIZE & SECURITY!

Description:
6 Year Old Home in Meridian Estate
This striking home is located in Dandenong’s newest and most sought-after estates Meridian and offers families generous space, quality fittings and great access to amenities. With beautiful and contemporary street appeal, the 6 year old Rawdon Hill built home gives families all the modern necessities including open plan living, master suite with full en suite and walk in robe, double lock up garage with remote access and direct internal entrance, formal lounge which can be transformed into cinema room, well equipped kitchen with island bench, 900 mm gas cook top, oven and canopy, dishwasher, stone bench tops, good sized pantry and glass splashbacks, central bathroom and separate toilet ideally placed adjacent to kids bedrooms and plenty of storage throughout with built in robes in all bedrooms. Additionally, this perfect family home boasts an array of features including central gas ducted heating, central evaporative cooling, monitored security alarm system, quality tiles through entire home besides bedrooms and formal lounge area where you will find carpets, downlights and pulldown blinds throughout. Externally the home is surrounded by beautifully kept gardens and lawns making maintenance a breeze, rear decked area and additional concrete patio which gives you the option to transform into stunning pergola with plumbing already incorporated. This home is seriously one of the best that you will see in the Dandenong area and fits the needs of any family who loves to entertain. Make sure that you arrange to inspect before it is too late!
Contact: Neb Delibasic on 0411 332 467
Auction: Saturday 21st April 2018 at 2:30pm, On Site
Terms: 10% Deposit, Balance in 120 Days

Description:
The right place - at the right time!
This beautifully presented 2 bedroom villa unit offers easy, everyday living in a very convenient location. Separate entry hall leading to a large sun-filled lounge room with wall to wall carpets, gas heating and air conditioning for year round comfort.
The kitchen has modern facilities with plenty of bench and cupboards space, gas cooking plus room for meals area. The unit features 2 large bedrooms both with built in robes, timber floor boards and the central family bathroom is well located near the bedrooms with separate shower, bath & toilet.
The unit allows low maintenance living without having to sacrifice outdoor space, featuring separate spacious laundry leading to private outdoor courtyard area and single lock up garage.
Located in a great location just minutes away from transport and central shops, Dandenong South Primary School, Andrews Reserve and Dandenong Bypass making access to major arterials a breeze.
Ideal first time investment and terrific for first time buyers or downsizers seeking low maintenance living at its best.

Conveying a private existence of a well-maintained unit in a group of 4, this immaculate single-level unit with own street access and no body corp fees is a peaceful sanctuary for those on the quest for a carefree lifestyle in a highly-convenient location.
Impeccably presented throughout, once you enter the home you will feel a sense of openness with the large rooms and nine foot ceilings.
Generous Lounge merges effortlessly with a modern Kitchen/Meals area, whilst 2 large Bedrooms provide plenty of room. To the rear, a maintenance free courtyard creates a secluded setting.
Other features include split system AC and single enclose carport with automatic roller door. With new carpets a fresh coat of paint and a recently renovated bathroom and kitchen, all you need to do is put in the furniture. A brilliant option to downsize, start-out or invest.
Located minutes to local shops, train stations, buses, Dandenong West Primary School and Greaves Reserve.
Insights: 1/7 Jones Road, Dandenong VIC 3175 was last sold in 2018.

Description:
Ground Floor Brilliance!
This is not your average apartment - here you get a sun soaked living room with a private balcony, three good sized bedrooms, two with BIRs, the master complete with its own balcony, ensuite and WIR, all while being so close to central Dandenong! It feels more like your own private oasis with the space, sunlight and extra features. You get comfortable living in a premium pocket of Dandenong and now it can be all yours!
You are so close to Dandenong Plaza, the shops, the cafes, restaurants and so much more. This is the meaning of Central Dandenong!
Head in via the secure entry where you're in pole position. On entry you have the dining room and living area. It's all overlooked by a kitchen that boasts stone benchtops, a dishwasher and stainless steel appliances, while enjoying easy access to the alfresco, perfect for entertaining. Completing the package inside are two robed BDRs, a central bathroom, split system invertor unit and a master bedroom fit for royalty.
Currently tenanted at $1521pcm, this can be an addition to your portfolio or a long term purchase. Call us today to make the most of this brilliant ground floor treat!

Description:
The dream starts here
First home buyers be the envy of your neighbours and friends by purchasing this 3 bedroom townhouse located centrally, yet in a wide and leafy street.
This residence is near completion and features:
-3 bedrooms with BIR's and quality carpets
-2 separate living areas
-Upstairs study nook
-Quality kitchen with gas HP's and s/s appliances
-Full bathroom with separate toilet
-Gas ducted heating and reverse cycle air conditioner
-Single lock up garage and rear courtyard
Completing this home are floating floorboards, quality tiles for the wet areas and access to the home from the garage.
Astute investors would benefit from a great rental return and generous depreciation schedule. FULL FIRST HOME OWNERS GRANT OF $10,000 APPLIES PLUS NO STAMP DUTY!
